title: Update and rename Bathroom.java to Room2.java
body:
Added: parameter to constructor to determine hiddenNum from frontDoorCode.
Added: extends Room.
Added: room description (top).
Changed: printEnter to printStart (to fit abstract class).
Moved variables to beginning of methods.
Changed: a bunch of stuff so that you could roam freely between the hallway and the bathroom after the initial escape (namely, added returning boolean).
Deleted: push/pullSink methods, put print() statements in switch.
Misc. edits to print() statements.

title: Update Room4.java
body:
Added description of the room (top).
Deleted imported library (unnecessary).
Added parameter to constructor: accepts frontDoorCode.
Deleted validateInt() method, replaced with Misc. method.
Added option to return to hall in constructor switch; choice validates from 0-3
Changed constructor do-while: loops while intent isn't to return to hallway (rather than hasKey).
Deleted hasKey when finding price tag in cupboard.
Misc. edits to commenting and print() statements.
